      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of this car, it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in absolute pristine condition\u2014spotless inside and out, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'm happy to chat, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
