    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including documented rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, ensuring the chassis dynamics are as sharp as the day it left Regensburg. An uncompromising example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
