    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine, collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior finish is deep and reflective, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been strictly garage-kept under a soft cover and has never seen a car wash brush or inclement weather. Inside, the cabin remains in a showroom state; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, the original floor mats are spotless, and the interior has never been smoked in. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It comes with a comprehensive binder of every service record, performed exclusively at authorized dealerships on a strict schedule. The tires have over 90% tread remaining, and the engine bay is detailed and free of any leaks or dust. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality. All original keys, owner's manuals, and the original window sticker are included in the sale.",
